      <scopecontent id="a3" encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Radio scripts written and broadcast in German to Austria by Peggy Sanford for Voice of America focusing on American customs, life, and culture between 1949 and 1966. Programs include "Peggy Sanford Plaudert" ("Peggy Sandford Chats"), "Looking Across the Ocean," "Schauplatz Amerika," "Klatsch und Tratsch aus Amerika," movie columns and women's features.</p>
      </scopecontent>
